10,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988362bf254c3e5f942e9f8581d159ca75ca6f57","tid":2035710,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"515私了便衣？無咩新聞講過？"},{"pid":"149c7365372b4dcfa2dc70a6f103e2fcffd8cacd","tid":2035710,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:48:46.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh"},{"pid":"b7dec846b7386440b66126a973f045b70b815242","tid":2035710,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e104b0663c98a28768505f3de28043d6893511c0","tid":2035710,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"鑽石山？"},{"pid":"cd841b7e3cf869897030f79f514cb72378913057","tid":2035710,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"988362bf254c3e5f942e9f8581d159ca75ca6f57","tid":2035710,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"515私了便衣？無咩新聞講過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"&quot;本月15日晚上約11時，據報1名休班警途經鑽石山龍蟠街8號對開時，發現5男1女在行人天橋上張貼海報，他制止無果，並懷疑被人噴噴霧膠水及拳打腳踢。該名休班警手、腳受傷，事後被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙警區反黑組接手追查後，昨日（25日）上午，於黃大仙美東邨某單位，以涉嫌「傷人」、「藏有工具可作非法用途」及「刑事毀壞」，拘捕姓林（27歲）男子，並即場檢獲4支懷疑與案有關的噴霧膠水。<br />\n<br />\n及至晚上，再於慈雲山慈民邨某單位，拘捕姓劉（21歲）男子，他涉嫌「傷人」及「刑事毀壞」。2人正被扣留調查。警方不排除有更多人被捕。&quot;<br />\nsource: 01"},{"pid":"d818eecbf0f2be925c05858b2f6544845007ea23","tid":2035710,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71f885ed0aec92335304928d